<p>If in "oncomplete" callback make setVal action with other masked input, you can see incorrect reactions in Chrome and Safary, well work in FF</p>  <pre><code>oncomplete: function(e){     $('.i-input-2').val($(e.currentTarget).inputmask('unmaskedvalue')); } </code></pre>  <p>Demo: <a href="http://jsfiddle.net/serGlazkov/nxLzq82o/" rel="nofollow">http://jsfiddle.net/serGlazkov/nxLzq82o/</a></p>